\psi(x) = \sum_{1\le n\le x} \Lambda(n)
E(x) = \psi(x) - x
 \sum_{F=1}^n \sum_{n/(F+1)<k\le n/F} \Lambda(k)[1-(\tfrac nk-F)][1-\tfrac kn(\tfrac nk-F)] = \frac1n \sum_{F=1}^n F \sum_{n/(F+1)<k\le n/F} \Lambda(k)[(F+1)k-n]. 
